0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:49:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n改變心態 真勇武"},{"pid":"d66987fd38687674a14641164fab89f35302057d","tid":1600600,"uid":113487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"43696d498505edabe402ca7d2e0b596352fc90b8","tid":1600600,"uid":282634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"再多再好既gear都不及思想上既武裝<br />\n香港人幾時先可以再向前行多步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dca9ba222ec78afa3910506d8cce2744c5bdbbf","tid":1600600,"uid":205752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:12:01.000Z","msg":"自推X9"},{"pid":"807ef48aa145b5ce12d1dea5ead50382639c945d","tid":1600600,"uid":205752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43696d498505edabe402ca7d2e0b596352fc90b8","tid":1600600,"uid":282634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"再多再好既gear都不及思想上既武裝<br />\n香港人幾時先可以再向前行多步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:12:44.000Z","msg":"啱，人數有，裝備都有，心態都有，但可以再進步"},{"pid":"968fde1dbe1730ef0eae276d3699c59247ebe789","tid":1600600,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1403efb6e245e22ee5329e08acd9233e3cd91d0","tid":1600600,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"E個真<br />\n唔可以再睇住手足比人拉<br />\n一定要反擊"},{"pid":"d13b48bf848c4ce3fdb18efde71ddacebd2d9d06","tid":1600600,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:21:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e85b2475ddc9d266b55623c8caacb8af9d888f0e","tid":1600600,"uid":315855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:30:50.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9868cb1bf886a56ec14d23